The update rule for the encoding matrix H\&. The formula used is
.PP
\[ H_{a\mu} \leftarrow H_{a\mu} \frac{\sum_{i} W_{ia} V_{i\mu}/(WH)_{i\mu}} {\sum_{k} H_{ka}} \].PP
